snippet.title: GOD EATER 3 - Multiplayer Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
During multiplayer, you and your friends can defeat powerful Ash Aragami online, play with customized heroes, and assemble up to 12 members in Assault Mode!

Rise above a world of desolation when GOD EATER 3 releases on Feb 8, 2019. Pre-Order today: bandainam.co/GE3PO #GodEater3 #BandaiNamco #VideoGames
